# 💳 AI-Powered Credit Risk Assessment Model

A machine learning application that predicts the probability of loan default using XGBoost, with an interactive Streamlit dashboard.

## 🚀 Features
- Predicts loan default probability with a risk gauge
- ROC Curve & AUC-ROC performance metrics
- Feature importance visualization
- Interactive borrower input form

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
Python | XGBoost | Scikit-learn | Streamlit | Plotly | Pandas

## 📊 Dataset
[Credit Risk Dataset - Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/laotse/credit-risk-dataset)

## ⚙️ Setup & Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python model.py        # Train and save the model
streamlit run app.py   # Launch the dashboard
```

## 📈 Model Performance
- Algorithm: XGBoost Classifier
- Metric: AUC-ROC Score ~0.93